data.description: FISHHAWK RANCH  SHOW STOPPER. Sitting on one of the Largest Lots with No Rear Neighbors! Steps away from the Community's LAKE HOUSE, Resort Style Parks and Pool! An impressive elevation this Sprawling One Story David Weekley is complemented with Barrell Tile Roof. Step inside and prepare yourself to Fall in Love you will quickly realize the sellers spared no expense designing this home with thousands in upgrades. Enter and your eyes are immediately drawn to the gorgeous flooring, plantation shutters and across the home to the expanded sliders at the back of the home to views of your private yard with plenty of room to add your dream pool. Enjoy relaxing outdoors on your expansive covered / screened lanai overlooking the spacious yard.. The Grenada is a popular floor plan that provides comfort and practicality for those who like to entertain, host family gatherings, work from home and more! Designed with distinction, 8ft doors, crown moldings, ceiling fans and soaring ceilings throughout. The kitchen is an absolute dream with quartz countertops, exquisite lighting, and gourmet appliance package. Your home office is dressed in French doors and offers built-ins. Check out the spacious Master Suite featuring a walk in closet, a private bath including frameless glass, super shower! All the secondary bedrooms are generously sized as well. This is Truly, A Must See- walking distances from Top Rated Barrington middle and Stowers Elementary schools. This home is an Energy Efficient Home w/double pane windows, tankless hot water & More!! Live like you are on Vacation Everyday! Fishhawk Award Winning/Resort Amenities include; Guest Parking, Fitness, Pool, Central Park and the Lake House with pool tables, ping pong, fire pit and More! Minutes to Tampa, MacDill AFB, Golf, World Class/Sugar Sand Beaches, Golf Courses & All that Florida has to Offer!
